{"tid":2187624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟被控暴動保釋候審生活Patreon(補番個人背景同現況)","createTime":"2020-09-03T17:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T07:18:10.000Z","uid":373491,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7749dd5bfcd8f03b9f5ae9d93b4d56e815e1a128","tid":2187624,"uid":373491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:45:33.000Z","msg":"講番背景先，其實我係一個二十頭讀緊大專既學生。公屋仔亦都係單親家庭，因為被捕既人實在太多，往往好似我呢啲唔出名嘅就好難得到支援。上年於11月被濫捕&mdash;被控暴動,而家已經上左3次庭,黎緊會由地院轉去區域法院。不過距離區院排期應該都係大半年，中間呢段空白期其實好辛苦。被限制離港，每星期去警署報到，受宵禁。全餐都真係幾難受。人都要為自己打算，除左番Parttine都想借Patreon呢個平台膽粗粗去做呢件認真創作既事,用相片同埋文字去紀錄低我呢段保釋候審緊既日常生活。兩個plan收費亦係十分十分貼地，頻度既收益會用於保釋候審呢段日子既生活費同讀書既學費。請大家支持一下!利申PM既話可以提供被告既證明,不是人血饅頭。同埋都希望同大家交流下[url]<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/join/hongkonger0501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fjoin%2Fhongkonger0501&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=18401d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/join/hongkonger0501</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4Kd9wp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4Kd9wp.jpg&h=a7ae3a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"6422c74aef4a2235b291bbd99adbbd6f02afd754","tid":2187624,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n<br />\n聽日再睇返詳情先"},{"pid":"8267f891c27a135f10b242777c6c356d2141aa10","tid":2187624,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"支持手足"},{"pid":"08cd0cbc287af66c07aa52c9813d9ab04b2a19b6","tid":2187624,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:46:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c735105ae05eeed38230ce3cc0ac62c5946f1b86","tid":2187624,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T17:49:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ee79b76733661c183c1a4e7f32549e0473b33bc","tid":2187624,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0